OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of rain will spread
OL,6,Fsoutheastwards, bringing some heavy
OL,7,Fbursts from mid-morning with a risk of
OL,8,Fthunder. Sunny spells then develop
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon, but also
OL,10,Fisolated, possibly heavy showers.
OL,11,FBreezy, especially on southern coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FHeavy showers clearing Kent,
OL,14,Fthen sunny spells for many this
OL,15,Fevening. A dry night follows with
OL,16,Fclear spells, but some showers
OL,17,Farriving by dawn. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
